summary:
We, Yael Mandl and Joe Shemesh own NC Paradise 
affiliate of Re/Max Golden North Cyprus 
offering high-quality residential homes and a comprehensive range of property services to European investors.
We are a team with a fresh, innovative approach to the real estate industry, offering unrivaled knowledge of the North Cyprus property sector, locations, and lifestyle.
NC Paradise together with Re/Max Golden North Cyprus brings a dynamic and diverse range of experience and expertise to the business, chosen for their professionalism, integrity and in-depth knowledge of the market.
